<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>رِوَايَةُ الْأَقْرَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨٣٣. وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْقُرَنَا»</span>: مَنِ اسْتَوَوْا فِي السَّنَدِ … وَالسِّنِّ غَالِباً، وَقِسْمَيْنِ اعْدُدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٨٣٤. <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُدَبَّجاً»</span>؛ وَهْوَ إِذَا كُلٌّ أَخَذْ … عَنْ آخَرٍ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَغَيْرَهُ:</span> انْفِرَادُ فَذّْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>